org.spongepowered.api.world.extent

Interface UnmodifiableBlockVolume

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BlockVolume
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ImmutableBlockVolume

    public interface UnmodifiableBlockVolume
extends BlockVolume
    A volume containing blocks that can be accessed but not modified. The data may be changed by other processes.
    See Also:
    BlockVolume
